DVD Description
We all love a good story, and no-one tells them better than Roly Mo, everybody's favourite mole. In this fantastic video there are stories galore, songs to get everyone dancing, and oodles of fun with Pom, Fimbo, Florrie and their friends. Featuring the episodes Baby's Rattle, Feather Duster and Lunch Bag, there are also specially recorded new scenes with Roly Mo in his library and even in his bath!

H.264 is a next-generation video compression format. H.264 is also known as MPEG-4 AVC. 
Developed for use in high definition systems such as HDTV, Blu-ray and HD DVD as well as low resolution portable devices such as Sony's PSP and Apple's iPod.
Even DivX/XviD is no match for H.264 - H.264 can often be 30% smaller than DivX/XviD and still offer the same quality video.
